        <DIV id="related_topics" style="position: relative; left: 0px; top: 0px; z-index: 0; display: none; ">相关文章: <SPAN class="close"><A href="http://www.javaeye.com/topic/113056#" onclick="$(&#39;related_topics&#39;).hide();return false;" title="关闭">&nbsp;</A></SPAN>
          <UL>
                            <LI><A href="http://www.javaeye.com/topic/55085" title="Ruby IDE for NetBeans 可以用了" target="_blank">Ruby IDE for NetBeans 可以用了</A></LI>
                              <LI><A href="http://www.javaeye.com/topic/274136" title="NetBeans6.5，焕然一新，革命性的变化，彻底打败eclipse大家都应该去试试" target="_blank">NetBeans6.5，焕然一新，革命性的变化，彻底打败eclipse大家都应该去试试</A></LI>
                              <LI><A href="http://www.javaeye.com/topic/57474" title="Windows平台的ruby IDE 点评" target="_blank">Windows平台的ruby IDE 点评</A></LI>
                          </UL>
            <BR><SPAN>推荐圈子: <A href="http://cpp-circle.group.javaeye.com/" target="_blank">C++语言</A></SPAN>
            <BR><A href="http://www.javaeye.com/wiki/topic/113056" target="_blank">更多相关推荐</A>
